Title: Jack Gets in the Game
Plot: When Jack discovers that his boss is retiring, he decides to get in the competition for his position. Meanwhile, Jenna begins to enjoy her fame for being fat and along with Jack encourages Liz to get her act together. Finally, Kenneth makes it his mission to get Tracy and Angie back together.
GuestStars: Erin Hilgartner, Marceline Hugot, Jean Morgan, Fajer Al-Kaisi, Matt Lauria
